title: Bobby Had To Save His Dog’s Life + Our No. 1 Favorite Show Moment of 2019 + Bobby’s Mailbag: Girlfriend is Texting Male Friend All-the-time
itunes:title: Bobby Had To Save His Dog’s Life + Our No. 1 Favorite Show Moment of 2019 + Bobby’s Mailbag: Girlfriend is Texting Male Friend All-the-time
description:
Bobby’s dog Stanley wasn't feeling well and was puking a lot so Bobby had to hop in and save his life. We’ve been counting down our Top 10 show moments of the year and today we reveal No. 1. Bobby opens up the Mailbag about a guy’s girlfriend who is now texting their male friend all the time. He wants to know if it’s weird…
